node.text:
Have you ever wondered what it takes to build a drive-able Bugatti Chiron entirely out of lego pieces? This amazing creation was built out of close to a million Lego technic pieces and is capable of driving under its own power.

How much do you think this thing costs? Let us know!

Song by CFM Production
#Lego #BugattiChiron #Bugatti #Chiron #Legos #FasterLiving

node.title: This Bugatti Chiron is built entirely out of LEGO

node.text:
Check out this Ferrari 360 Challenge Stradale we saw at the Heveningham Concours! The Stradale is a track-focused and more aggressive iteration of the 360 Modena. Stay tuned until the end to see some crazy donuts and powerslides! Is this the best sounding Ferrari ever? Comment below!

http://fasterliving.com/
